programme.desc: Three potheads sell a strain of magical weed to raise funds for their friend's funeral.

programme.title: Bridesmaids
programme.desc: Annie's life is a mess. But when she finds out her lifelong best friend is engaged, she simply must serve as Lillian's maid of honour.

programme.title: Storks
programme.desc: Storks have moved on from delivering babies to packages. But when an order for a baby appears, the best delivery stork must scramble to fix the error by delivering the baby.

programme.title: Pitch Perfect
programme.desc: Beca, a freshman at her new college, finds herself muscled into a clique whose only thing in common is how good they sound when they sing together in perfect harmony in this laugh-out-loud comedy.

programme.title: Mamma Mia!
programme.desc: Sophie has just one wish to make her wedding perfect: to have her father walk her down the aisle. Now she just has to find out who he is.

programme.title: Grumpy Old Men
programme.desc: When a lonely, flamboyant, middle-aged widow moves in across the street from them, the male rivalry between two neighbours begins.

programme.title: Couples Retreat

programme.title: It's Complicated
programme.desc: With a thriving bakery, a new romance and her divorce finally behind her, Jane Adler has her life all figured out, until her ex-husband Jake decides he'll stop at nothing to win her back.

programme.title: Parenthood
programme.desc: An unforgettable and hilarious portrait of life's most rewarding occupation: Parenthood. The Buckmans are a modern-day family facing the age-old dilemma of trying to raise children the right way.

programme.title: The Boy Next Door
programme.desc: A newly separated teacher gives in to temptation when the handsome teenager next door attempts to seduce her. But trouble ensues when she tries to end the relationship.

programme.title: Snitch
programme.desc: In the fast-paced action thriller, a father goes undercover as an informant and infiltrates a drug cartel on a dangerous mission risking everything to save his son from going to prison.

programme.title: For Love Of The Game

programme.title: 2 Fast 2 Furious

programme.title: Puss in Boots

programme.title: A Cinderella Story

programme.title: Night School

programme.title: American Pie: The Wedding

programme.title: 8 Mile
